show.description: When Jiang Yueqing's daughter dies in a kindergarten collapse, her husband, Ji Bo Ran, prioritizes saving his first love's child instead. Devastated by his absence at the funeral and uncovering his betrayal, Jiang Yueqing files for divorce and plots her revenge.
